		</audio>
		<reader oae-label="Reading text (optional)." oae-type="textarea" oae-rows="10">
			<![CDATA[]]>
		</reader>
		<text oae-label="Text" oae-type="textarea" oae-rows="15">
			<![CDATA[<b>A:</b>	Hi, Jackie.  How <blank word="was" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>be</i>) your weekend?
<b>B:</b>	I <blank word="didn't do;did not do"/> (<i>not do</i>) anything special.  On Saturday morning, I <blank word="cleaned"/> 
      (<i>clean</i>) the house and <blank word="went" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>go</i>) shopping for food. 
	In the afternoon, the weather <blank word="was" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>be</i>) sunny and warm.  I <blank word="played" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>play</i>) soccer with my friends.
<b>A:</b>	What about Sunday?
<b>B:</b>	I <blank word="watched"/> (<i>watch</i>) a movie on TV.  I also <blank word="took" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>take</i>) a nap in the afternoon.  
	What <blank word="did" blanksize="Small"/> you <blank word="do" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>do</i>)?
<b>A:</b>	I <blank word="didn't do;did not do"/> (<i>not do</i>) much on Saturday.  I <blank word="read" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>read</i>) a book and <blank word="listened"/> 
      (<i>listen</i>) to music.  On Sunday, I <blank word="cooked" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>cook</i>) dinner for my friends. 
<b>B:</b>	What <blank word="did" blanksize="Small"/> you <blank word="make" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>make</i>)?
<b>A:</b>	I <blank word="got" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>get</i>) a new recipe from my sister.  I <blank word="made" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>make</i>) fish, vegetables, and rice. 
<b>B:</b>	That sounds delicious.
<b>A:</b>	My friends <blank word="liked" blanksize="Small"/> (<i>like</i>) it.]]>
		</text>
	</page>
